---
import ListItem from '../../components/text/ListItem.astro'
import Card from '../../components/ui/Card.astro'
import PageHeader from '../../components/ui/PageHeader.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Therapeutic Bodywork">
  <PageHeader>
    <h1 class="text-primary lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">Therapeutic Bodywork</h1>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-(--site-padding-base)">
      <div class="prose text-neutral-content">
        <p class="lsa lsa-slide-up delay-100 no-repeat">
          At Madison Lymphatics and Bodywork, we have extensive knowledge and experience treating a
          wide range of musculoskeletal conditions. We always focus on the patient's individual
          needs, analyzing range of motion, looking at posture, and zeroing in on the muscles and
          soft tissues that may be affected.
        </p>
        <p class="lsa lsa-slide-up delay-200 no-repeat">
          We believe that educating our clients on their pain and what may be causing it is
          imperative to recovery with therapeutic massage.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="prose text-neutral-content">
        <p class="lsa lsa-slide-up delay-300 no-repeat">
          Whether you're seeking relief from chronic pain, recovering from an injury, or simply
          looking to enhance your overall well-being, our therapeutic bodywork services are designed
          to meet your specific needs and promote healing.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lsa lsa-slide-up delay-400 no-repeat">
      <a
        href="https://booksy.com/en-us/689566_madison-lymphatics-and-bodywork_massage_39663_madison"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn btn-primary"
      >
        Book Now
      </a>
    </div>
  </PageHeader>

  <main>
    <!-- Therapeutic Massage Section -->
    <section id="therapeutic-massage" class="pt-0">
      <div class="wrapper container lg:max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
        <h2
          class="h1 font-bold text-primary mb-(--site-padding-md) text-center lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat"
        >
          Therapeutic Massage
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-center mb-12 mx-auto lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">
          Therapeutic massage is an extremely useful tool for treating hundreds of injury, pain, and
          stress-related conditions and can:
        </p>

        <ul
          class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-(--site-padding-base) w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto"
        >
          <div class="list">
            <ListItem
              number={1}
              listItemClass="text-base-content"
              text="Alleviate low-back pain, sciatica pain and improve range of motion"
            />
            <ListItem
              number={2}
              listItemClass="text-base-content"
              text="Relieve migraine and headache pain"
            />
            <ListItem
              number={3}
              listItemClass="text-base-content"
              text="Exercise and stretch weak, tight, or atrophied muscles"
            />
            <ListItem
              number={4}
              listItemClass="text-base-content"
              text="Help athletes of any level prepare for, and recover from, strenuous workouts"
            />

            <!-- Mobile only -->
            <ListItem
              number={5}
              listItemClass="md:hidden text-base-content"
              text="Provide pain relief and facilitate healing after work- and car- related accidents"
            />
            <ListItem
              number={6}
              listItemClass="md:hidden text-base-content"
              text="Reduce post surgery adhesions and swelling"
            />
            <ListItem
              number={7}
              listItemClass="md:hidden text-base-content"
              text="Reduce pain and discomfort associated with TMJ, carpal tunnel syndrome, fibromyalgia, and chronic fatigue syndrome"
            />
            <ListItem
              number={8}
              listItemClass="md:hidden text-base-content"
              text="Provide support for physical therapy sessions"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Desktop only -->
          <div class="list hidden md:block">
            <ListItem
              number={5}
              listItemClass="text-base-content"
              text="Provide pain relief and facilitate healing after work- and car- related accidents"
            />
            <ListItem
              number={6}
              listItemClass="text-base-content"
              text="Reduce post surgery adhesions and swelling"
            />
            <ListItem
              number={7}
              listItemClass="text-base-content"
              text="Reduce pain and discomfort associated with TMJ, carpal tunnel syndrome, fibromyalgia, and chronic fatigue syndrome"
            />
            <ListItem
              number={8}
              listItemClass="text-base-content"
              text="Provide support for physical therapy sessions"
            />
          </div>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Relaxation Massage Section -->
    <section id="relaxation-massage" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/70 to-secondary/80">
      <div class="wrapper container lg:max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="h1 mb-8 text-secondary-content text-center lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">
          Relaxation Massage
        </h2>
        <p
          class="text-lg text-secondary-content md:text-xl text-center mb-12 mx-auto lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat"
        >
          In contrast, relaxation massage is beneficial to the
          <a href="/blog/parasympathetic-nervous-system/" class="link"
            >parasympathetic nervous system</a
          > and can:
        </p>

        <ul
          class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-(--site-padding-base) w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto"
        >
          <div class="list">
            <ListItem
              listItemClass="text-secondary-content"
              number={1}
              text="Relax and soften injured, tired, and overused muscles"
            />
            <ListItem
              listItemClass="text-secondary-content"
              number={2}
              text="Pump oxygen and nutrients into tissues and vital organs, improving circulation"
            />
            <ListItem
              listItemClass="text-secondary-content"
              number={3}
              text="Lessen depression and anxiety"
            />
            <ListItem
              listItemClass="text-secondary-content"
              number={4}
              text="Improve the condition of the body's largest organ—the skin"
            />

            <!-- Mobile only -->
            <ListItem
              listItemClass="md:hidden text-secondary-content"
              number={5}
              text="Enhance immunity by stimulating lymph flow—the body's natural defense system"
            />
            <ListItem
              listItemClass="md:hidden text-secondary-content"
              number={6}
              text="Promote tissue regeneration, reducing scar tissue and stretch marks"
            />
            <ListItem
              listItemClass="md:hidden text-secondary-content"
              number={7}
              text="Release endorphins—amino acids that work as the body's natural painkiller"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Desktop only -->
          <div class="list hidden md:block">
            <ListItem
              listItemClass="text-secondary-content"
              number={5}
              text="Enhance immunity by stimulating lymph flow—the body's natural defense system"
            />
            <ListItem
              listItemClass="text-secondary-content"
              number={6}
              text="Promote tissue regeneration, reducing scar tissue and stretch marks"
            />
            <ListItem
              listItemClass="text-secondary-content"
              number={7}
              text="Release endorphins—amino acids that work as the body's natural painkiller"
            />
          </div>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Section -->
    <section id="pricing">
      <div class="wrapper container lg:max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="mb-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <h2 class="h1 text-secondary mb-3 lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">Pricing</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- 30 Minutes -->
            <div class="lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat flex">
              <Card
                id="30-minute-session"
                className="text-center border border-base-300 hover:border-secondary"
              >
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-(--site-padding-base)">
                  <h3>30 Minutes</h3>
                  <span class="h2 font-bold text-secondary">$55</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-base-content/80">
                    The perfect session length for working on a specific area only, i.e.:
                    headache/migraine relief, tense neck and shoulder muscles.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-actions justify-center mt-auto">
                  <a
                    href="https://booksy.com/en-us/689566_madison-lymphatics-and-bodywork_massage_39663_madison"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="btn btn-secondary w-full"
                  >
                    Book Now
                  </a>
                </div>
              </Card>
            </div>
            <!-- 60 Minutes -->
            <div class="lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat flex">
              <Card
                id="60-minute-session"
                className="text-center scale-[1.02] border-2 border-secondary"
              >
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-(--site-padding-base)">
                  <h3>60 Minutes</h3>
                  <span class="h2 font-bold text-secondary">$110</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-base-content/80">
                    A good choice for those seeking 2-3 areas of focus, i.e.: neck/shoulder/back
                    pain, lower back/hip tension, or more chronic issues like sciatica.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-actions justify-center mt-auto">
                  <a
                    href="https://booksy.com/en-us/689566_madison-lymphatics-and-bodywork_massage_39663_madison"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="btn btn-secondary w-full"
                  >
                    Book Now
                  </a>
                </div>
              </Card>
            </div>
            <!-- 90 Minutes -->
            <div class="lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat flex">
              <Card
                id="90-minute-session"
                className="text-center border border-base-300 hover:border-secondary"
              >
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-(--site-padding-base)">
                  <h3>90 Minutes</h3>
                  <span class="h2 font-bold text-secondary">$165</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-base-content/80">
                    A full body massage can be done thoroughly with the therapist concentrating on
                    several specific areas of tension
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-actions justify-center mt-auto">
                  <a
                    href="https://booksy.com/en-us/689566_madison-lymphatics-and-bodywork_massage_39663_madison"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="btn btn-secondary w-full"
                  >
                    Book Now
                  </a>
                </div>
              </Card>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section
      id="therapeutic-bodywork-cta"
      class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-secondary/10"
    >
      <div class="wrapper container lg:max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">To schedule Massage Therapy:</h2>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
            <div class="lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">
              <a
                href="https://booksy.com/en-us/689566_madison-lymphatics-and-bodywork_massage_39663_madison"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="btn btn-primary"
              >
                Book Now
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">
              <a href="tel:608-203-8550" class="btn btn-dash"> Call 608-203-8550 </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
